          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> be a semidirected subset of a <fr:link href="jms-001S.xml" title="Pointed dcpo" addr="jms-001S" type="local">pointed</fr:link> dcpo <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>; then the intersection <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[I \cap  A^+]]></fr:tex> is semidirected, where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A^+]]></fr:tex> is the <fr:link href="jms-001P.xml" title="The subdcpo spanned by positive elements" addr="jms-001P" type="local">subdcpo spanned by positive elements</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
